column2: I'm signing because is that Johnny Depp truly 100% deserves another chance to be reinstated by Disney to return to the role of Captain Jack Sparrow of Pirates Of The Caribbean 6.  And I think that Disney were totally wrong to dismiss Johnny in the first place for the wrongful misunderstanding, because that horrible narcissistic witch Amber was the true abuser.  Please, Please Disney give Johnny another chance.  Johnny will always will be Captain Jack Sparrow.

column51: Give the Pirate role back to Johnny Depp.
column52:
Let's petition to get Johnny Depp back in "Pirate's of the Caribbean." Johnny Depp was dropped from the "Pirates of the Caribbean" franchise because of the domestic abuse allegations made by his ex-wife Amber Heard. As of yesterday, June 1, 2022, Johnny Depp was proven to be innocent. Johnny Depp won the defamation suit against his ex-wife Amber Heard after the jury found that she had defamed Johnny Depp by saying that he abused her over the course of their relationship. Disney dropped Johnny Depp from the roll just days after Amber Heard's false allegations were made. Now that he has been proven innocent by the Judge and Jury let's get Johnny back into the "Pirates of the Caribbean."

Disney has always been so quick to judge others and it needs to Stop. What happened to innocent until proven guilty? Disney didn't even give Johnny Depp a chance to respond to Heard's allegations. They need to remember there's TWO sides to every story not just One. Disney obviously should know this better then everyone else because of their numerous remakes depicting both sides to the "villains" story's such a "Cruella" or "The Evil Queen" from "Snow White". How many murderous "villains" have they created that have been glorified over the years. You don't see Disney banishing the "Evil Queen"  from "Snow White" for practically killing Snow with poisoned apples. Or Cruella for wanting to kill the dalmatians to turn into fur coats. Another good example is Disney's "Once Upon a Time" you see both sides to the "villains" stories and in the end you see there not villains at all. They are just people Disney has labeled as "Villains" who have been misunderstood. Johnny Depp is not the true "villain" of this story it is Amber Heard who has made false allegations about him. So she should be banned from Disney not Johnny Depp. With that said please sign this petition to get Johnny Depp back into "Pirates of the Caribbean". We will be sending this petition over to Disney, so please make sure to sign it. Every signature helps!! We all know there is only one Captain Jack Sparrow and his name is Johnny Depp!! 

If Disney doesn't realize there mistakes then maybe we need to banish them from our wallets.

column54:
Give the Pirate role back to Johnny Depp. Let's petition to get Johnny Depp back in "Pirate's of the Caribbean". Johnny Depp was dropped from the "Pirates of the Caribbean" franchise because of the domestic abuse allegations made by his ex-wife Amber Heard. As of yesterday June 1, 2022 Johnny Depp was proven to be innocent. Johnny Depp won the defamation suit against his ex-wife Amber Heard after the jury found that she had defamed Johnny Depp by saying that he abused her over the course of their relationship. Disney dropped Johnny Depp from the roll just days after Amber Heard's false allegations were made. Now that he has been proven innocent by the Judge and Jury let's get Johnny back into the "Pirates of the Caribbean".
 
Disney has always been so quick to judge others and it needs to Stop. What happened to innocent until proven guilty? Disney didn't even give Johnny Depp a chance to respond to Heard's allegations. They need to remember there's TWO sides to every story not just One. Which they should know by now from all the remakes of there movies they have done where it shows both sides to the "villains" story's such a "Cruella" or "The Evil Queen" from "Snow White". How many murderous "villains" have they created that have been glorified over the years. You don't see Disney banishing the "Evil Queen"  from "Snow White" for practically killing Snow with poisoned apples. Or Cruella for wanting to kill the dalmatians to turn into fur coats. Another good example is Disney's "Once Upon a Time" you see both sides to the "villains" stories and in the end you see there not villains at all. They are just people Disney has labeled as "Villains" who have been misunderstood. Johnny Depp is not the true "villain" of this story it is Amber Heard who has made false allegations about him. So she should be banned from Disney not Johnny Depp. With that said please sign this petition to get Johnny Depp back into "Pirates of the Caribbean". We will be sending this petition over to Disney, so please make sure to sign it. Every signature helps!! We all know there is only one Captain Jack Sparrow and his name is Johnny Depp!! 
If Disney doesn't realize there mistakes then maybe we need to banish them from our wallets.
